(33,	'05822',	'同义词\n\n   见 blepo  的定义          991\n   见 horao  的定义         3708\n   见 skopeo 的定义         4648\n\n对照 991, 3708\n\n   3708着重的是辨识的心,991则是着重特殊的情绪.除却生理层面,\n   3708指一般性的观察(出于视觉的),重点在于精神层面.910则是\n   指纯粹的外在观看. \n\n对照 991, 4648\n\n   4648的观看比991深刻,通常意谓\"仔细搜寻观察\".除却生理层面,\n   4648的意思是为了得到某一东西,\"定睛于,全神贯注于\"该目标.\n   所以也就是\"对准目标,关注\"的意思',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of blepo 991\n See definition of horao 3708\n See definition of skopeo 4648\n\nComparison 991, 3708\n\n 3708 focuses on the discerning mind, while 991 focuses on special emotions. Apart from the physiological aspect,\n 3708 refers to general observation (visual), with emphasis on the spiritual dimension. 910 is\n Refers to purely outward viewing. \n\nComparison 991, 4648\n\n The viewing of 4648 is deeper than 991, and is usually meant to be “carefully searched and observed”. Apart from the physiological aspect,\n 4648 means to get something, “set your eyes on, focus on” that goal.\n So that\'s the meaning of “aim, focus on”',	1),
