(324,	'05868',	'同义词\n\n   见 paidarion 的定义      3808\n   见 paidion   的定义      3813\n   见 paidiske  的定义      3814\n   见 pais      的定义      3816\n   见 teknon    的定义      5043\n   见 huios     的定义      5207\n\n   3813 - 专指小孩子\n   3808 - 囊括至第一年上学的孩子\n   3816 - 指任何年龄的孩子\n   3814 - 指将近青少年的孩子\n\n   3816, 5043 的意思,从年龄或后裔的角度来看是相似的,\n   不过前者比起3813,更包含年纪大一点的.3816的年龄期\n   则不是很明确. \n\n对照 5043, 5207\n\n   5043 - 特别强调身世的物质与外在层面\n   5207 - 特别强调身世的内在,伦理,法律层面',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of paidarion 3808\n See definition of paidion 3813\n See definition of paidiske 3814\n See definition of pais 3816\n See definition of teknon 5043\n See definition of huios 5207\n\n 3813 - Refers to children\n 3808 - Including children in the first year of school\n 3816 - Refers to children of any age\n 3814 - Refers to children who are close to teenagers\n\n The meanings of 3816, 5043 are similar in terms of age or descent,\n However, the former includes an older one than 3813. The age range of 3816\n then it\'s not very clear. \n\nComparison 5043, 5207\n\n 5043 - Emphasis is placed on the material and external dimensions of the body\n 5207 - Special emphasis on the intrinsic, ethical, and legal aspects of life',	1),
