(576,	'05874',	'同义词\n\n   见 tereo           5083\n   见 phulasso        5442\n\n   5083 - \"看守或遵守\"\n   5442 - \"看守\"\n\"\n\n   5083 表达一种机警的看顾, 暗示是现在所拥有的.\n   5442 表示一种完全的保护, 通常暗示是由外而来的攻击. \n   5083 可说是结果, 而5442 则是方法.',	'synonyms\n\n See tereo 5083\n See phulasso 5442\n\n 5083 - “Watchful or Compliant”\n 5442 - “caretaker”\n“\n\n 5083 expresses a kind of vigilant care, implying that it is now owned.\n 5442 indicates a complete form of protection, usually implying an external attack. \n 5083 can be said to be the result, while 5442 is the method.',	1),
