(623,	'05784',	'5784 语态 - 主动\n\n    主动语态表示主词所代表的这个人是动词的动作的行动者，或是执行者．\n　　例：”这男孩打这球”，表示这个男孩是打球的人．',	'5784 Voice - Active\n\n The active voice indicates that the person represented by the subject is the actor or executor of the action of the verb.\n Example: “This boy plays this ball” means that the boy is the one who plays the ball.',	1),
