(708,	'05143',	'5143 trecho {trekh\'-o}\n\n显然是一原形动词 (适当地说是 threcho, 参见 2359),以 dremo {drem\'-o}(1408 的字源)\n作为在某些时态时的替代字; TDNT - 8:226,1189; 动词\n\nAV - run 19, have course 1; 20\n\n1) 奔跑, 匆促, 前进\n2) (灵性,心智上) 努力, 尽力\n2) 隐喻,指迅速开展 (#帖后 3:1|)  ',	'5143 trecho {trekh\'-o}\n\nApparently a primitive verb (appropriately threcho, see 2359), in dremo {drem\'-o} (origin 1408)\nAs an alternative word in certain tenses; TDNT - 8:226 ,1189; verb\n\nAV - run 19, have course 1; 20\n\n1) Run, hurry, move forward\n2) Work hard (spiritually, mentally) and do your best\n2) Metaphor, refers to rapid development (#帖后 3:1 |)',	1),
