(717,	'05794',	'5794 语气 - 命令\n\n    希腊文中的命令语气, 相当于英文中的祈使语语气, 表示以一个命令或者权威,\n    令听命者执行某项行动.T因此, 耶稣说: 你们当悔改, 信福音\" (可1:15)\n    不是一项邀请, 而是一项绝对的命令, 要求所有听到这个命令的人, 完全顺服.',	'5794 Tone - Command\n\n The command tone in Greek, which is equivalent to the tone of prayer in English, indicates that an order or authority,\n To cause the hearers to perform an action. T Therefore, Jesus said, “Repent and believe in the gospel” (May 1:15)\n Not an invitation, but an absolute order, requiring everyone who hears this order, to be completely obedient.',	1),
