(809,	'05862',	'同义词\n\n   见 metamellomai 的定义   3338\n   见 metanoeo 的定义       3340\n\n   一般认为两者的区别在于3338指情绪上的改变,3340是选择的改变.\n   3338提到某些具体点,3340涵盖整个生命.3338不过是后悔或懊悔,\n   3340则是道德上的转变,亦即悔改.3340的含意更完整,更尊贵,表达\n   的是道德行动与议题,使用的比率也远为高,而且常以祈使语态出现.',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of metamellomai 3338\n See definition of metanoeo 3340\n\n It is generally accepted that the difference between the two is that 3338 refers to a change in mood and 3340 is a change in choice.\n 3338 refers to specific points and 3340 covers the whole of life.3338 is nothing more than regret or remorse,\n 3340 is a moral transformation, that is, repentance. The meaning of 3340 is more complete, more honorable, and expressed\n are moral actions and issues, which are used at a much higher rate and often appear in the form of prayers.',	1),
