(3215,	'05812',	'同义词\n\n   见 apokalupto       601\n   见 delos           1212\n   见 phaneroo        5319\n\n对照 5319, 601\n\n   5319是描述外在的显示,而且是显给所有人的;601则是对思想的信徒\n   所作的内在显示,而且是常存的.601的\"揭示\"先于5319,产生出5319\n   的\"彰显\";前者看的是被揭示的对象,后者看的是得到启示的人.不过\n   也有人质疑这种解释 \n\n比较 5319, 1212\n\n   1212 - 明显的, 知道或理解的\n   5319 - 彰显, 相对于隐藏或不可见的\n\n   1212指的是内在的认知, 5319指的是外在的样式',	'synonyms\n\n See apokalupto 601\n See Delos 1212\n See phaneroo 5319\n\nComparison 5319, 601\n\n 5319 describes an outward display and is visible to all; 601 is a believer in the idea\n The intrinsic indication is made and is a constant one. The “reveal” of 601 precedes 5319 and produces 5319\n “manifest”; the former looks at the object revealed, and the latter looks at the revealed person.\n There are also people who question this interpretation \n\ncomparison 5319, 1212\n\n 1212 - obvious, known or understood\n 5319 - Highlight, as opposed to hidden or invisible\n\n 1212 refers to inner cognition, 5319 refers to external patterns',	1),
