(3252,	'00000',	'中文用几个字翻译一个希伯来或希腊原文字，而且这几个字之间有其他原文字穿插。\n\n\n例1: #赛 59:9|\n\n原文编号 05381  中文圣经\n追上                     追<05381><00>不<03808>上<05381>\n\n例2：#太 15:23|\n\n原文编号630            中文圣经\n\n打发走                       打发 <630><00>他<846>走<630>\n\n\n 00代表原文只用了一次5381或630，但是在翻译的时候被其他原文字间隔开来',	'Chinese uses a few words to translate an original Hebrew or Greek script, and there are other original words interspersed between these words.\n\n\nExample 1: #赛 59:9 |\n\nOriginal number 05381 Chinese Bible\nCan\'t catch up\n\nExample 2: #太 15:23 |\n\nOriginal text number 630 Chinese Bible\n\nSend him away Send him away\n\n\n 00 means that the original text is only used once 5381 or 630, but it is spaced apart by other original texts at the time of translation',	1),
(3253,	'05823',	'同义词\n\n   见 boao     的定义        994\n   见 kaleo    的定义       2564\n   见 krazo    的定义       2896\n   见 kraugazo  的定义      2905\n\n    994 - 呼喊表达情感,特别是求助\n   2564 - 为着一个目的呼喊\n   2896 - 模糊,嘶喊的声音大叫\n   2905 - 2896的加强语气, 声音沙哑地呼叫,表达轻篾等情绪\n\n   2564 牵涉到聪智; 994 感受; 2896 直觉',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of boao 994\n See definition of kaleo 2564\n See definition of krazo 2896\n See definition of kraugazo 2905\n\n 994 - Shouting to express emotions, especially for help\n 2564 - Shout for a Purpose\n 2896 - Blurry, screaming voice\n 2905 - 2896 to strengthen the tone, call with a husky voice, and express emotions such as light cynicism\n\n 2564 Involves Wisdom; 994 Feeling; 2896 Intuition',	1),
(3254,	'05811',	'同义词\n\n   见 anthropoktonos 的定义      443\n   见 sikarios       的定义     4607\n   见 phoneus        的定义     5406\n\n5406 任何的 \"谋杀\" \n4607 \"刺杀\" \n443  在新约中有特别的强调',	'synonyms\n\n See the definition of anthropoktonos 443\n See definition of sikarios 4607\n See definition of phoneus 5406\n\n5406 Any “murder” \n4607 “Assassination” \n443 Special emphasis is placed in the New Testament',	1),
(3255,	'05804',	'同义词\n\n   见 alalazo 的定义         214\n   见 dakruo  的定义        1145\n   见 threneo 的定义        2354\n   见 klaio   的定义        2799\n   见 odurmos 的定义        3602\n   见 stenazo 的定义        4727\n\n    214 - 以东方习俗哀哭,以近乎礼仪的方式嚎啕大哭.\n   1145 - 流泪,无声哭泣\n   2354 - 用正式的方法表达哀伤,唱哀歌\n   2799 - 出声哭泣,像孩童一般地哭\n   3602 - 以言词表达哀伤, 哀悼\n   4727 - 以含混的声音或是哀吟表达哀伤',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of alalazo 214\n See definition of dakruo 1145\n See definition of threneo 2354\n See definition of klaio 2799\n See definition of odurmos 3602\n See definition of stenazo 4727\n\n 214 - Wailing in oriental customs, crying in an almost ceremonial way.\n 1145 - To tears, to cry silently\n 2354 - Express sadness in a formal way, sing mourning songs\n 2799 - Cry loudly, cry like a child\n 3602 - Express sadness and mourning in words\n 4727 - Expressing sadness in a vague voice or mourning',	1),
(3256,	'05833',	'同义词\n\n   见 diadema    的定义     1238\n   见 stephanos  的定义     4735\n\n   1238 - 皇室用的冠冕\n   4735 - 像拉丁文的 \"corona\", 是花冠或花圈, \n          象徵在比赛或战役中得着胜利, 也象\n          徵在婚礼中的喜悦, 或节庆中的欢乐',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of diadema 1238\n See definition of stephanos 4735\n\n 1238 - Crown for the royal family\n 4735 - Like the Latin “corona”, is a wreath or wreath, \n It symbolizes victory in a game or battle, as well as\n The joy of a wedding, or the joy of a festival',	1),
(3257,	'05826',	'同义词\n\n   见 gnosis   的定义       1108\n   见 sophia   的定义       4678\n   见 sunesis  的定义       4907\n   见 phronesis  的定义     5428\n\n比较 1108 4678\n\n   1108指的是知识本身,4678则是指行动所展现的智慧.\n   1108主要用于真理的领悟,4678则加上论述真理,与追\n   溯真理之间的关系那股能力.\n\n比较 4678, 4907, 5428\n\n   4678 - 理解细节\"最杰出的聪智\"\n   4907 - 剖析,理解事情的肌理\n   5428 - 实际的,其中隐含行动',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of gnosis 1108\n See definition of sophia 4678\n See definition of sunesis 4907\n See definition of phronesis 5428\n\nCompare 1108 4678\n\n 1108 refers to knowledge itself, and 4678 refers to wisdom in action.\n 1108 is mainly used for the understanding of truth, and 4678 is added to talk about the truth, and chasing\n That ability of the relationship between retrospective truth.\n\nCompare 4678, 4907, 5428\n\n 4678 - Understanding the Details “The Most Outstanding Intelligence”\n 4907 - Anatomy, Understanding the Texture of Things\n 5428 - Actual, in which actions are implied',	1),
(3258,	'05813',	'同义词\n\n   见 apostello        649\n   见 pempo           3992\n\n   3992 - 是一个论到 \"差遣\"的一般用言; 可能隐含有一起差遣者 (如: 由上帝差遣)\n    649 - 包含有关差遣所需要的装备, 即被差者的职份或权威',	'synonyms\n\n See apostello 649\n See pempo 3992\n\n 3992 - is a general term for “dispatch”; may imply a person sent together (e.g., sent by God)\n 649 - Contain equipment required for the mission, i.e. the position or authority of the person being sent',	1),
