(3336,	'05830',	'同义词\n\n   见 despotes  的定义      1203\n   见 kurios    的定义      2962\n\n   1203 - 单与奴隶有关, 指绝对所有权及无法掌控的势力\n   2962 - 具有较广泛的意义, 可使用于各种等级的人际关系里, 并无财产所有权或专制绝对的涵义',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of despotes 1203\n See definition of kurios 2962\n\n 1203 - Relating solely to slaves, refers to absolute ownership and uncontrollable forces\n 2962 - Has a broader meaning, can be used in interpersonal relationships of all levels and has no absolute meaning of property ownership or authoritarianism',	1),
(3337,	'05815',	'同义词\n\n   见 arti             737\n   见 ede             2235\n   见 nun             3568\n\n    737 - \"刚刚, 现在, 从现在开始\", 指的是很接近现在的时间; 稍后完全指现在的时间.\n   2235 - \"现在 (已经)\", 指的是其他的时间, 期待的时刻, 是主观或想像中的现在.\n   3568 - \"现在\", 指的是一个确定的点, 或一段时间, (客观的) 立刻的现在',	'synonyms\n\n See arti 737\n see ede 2235\n see nun 3568\n\n 737 - “Just now, from now on” refers to a time very close to the present; later refers to the present time entirely.\n 2235 - “Now (already)”, refers to other times, moments of anticipation, that are subjective or imagined in the present.\n 3568 - “Now” means a definite point, or a period of time, (objective) immediate present',	1),
(3338,	'05819',	'同义词\n\n   见 baros            922\n   见 ogkos           3591\n   见 phortion        5413\n\n922  和重量有关\n3591 和容积有关, 可能受到压迫而致;\n922  是指重担, 而5413 指的是可承担这重担, 它可轻可重',	'synonyms\n\n See baros 922\n See ogkos 3591\n See ph5413\n\n922 has to do with weight\n3591 is volume-related and may be caused by oppression;\n922 means a burden, and 5413 means that the burden can be borne, it can be light or heavy',	1),
