(3355,	'05864',	'同义词\n\n   见 miaino          3392\n   见 moluno          3435\n\n   3392, \"弄脏, 污点\", 和 3435 \"弄脏, 沾污\" 不同, 后者不但指其本身\n   且是外在的弄脏; 3392 有时可用于好的方面, 但 3435 则没有价值\n   has no worthy reference',	'synonyms\n\n See miaino 3392\n See moluno 3435\n\n 3392, “soiled, stained”, and 3435 “soiled, contaminated”, which refers not only to itself\n and external soiling; 3392 can sometimes be used for good, but 3435 is worthless\n has no worthy reference',	1),
(3356,	'05865',	'同义词\n\n   见 morphe          3444\n   见 schema          4976\n\n   3444 \"形象\" 不同于 4976 \"形状, 形象, 样式\", \n   3444 指的是内在的和本质, 而4976则是外在和非本质的. \n        #腓 2:7| 指出耶稣基督有完全的仆人的形象; \n   4976 指的是外在的, 就是 #腓 2:8| 的人的身体',	'synonyms\n\n See morphe 3444\n See schema 4976\n\n 3444 “Image” is different from 4976 “Shape, Image, Style”, \n 3444 refers to the intrinsic and intrinsic, while 4976 refers to the external and non-essential. \n #腓 2:7 | Point out that Jesus Christ has the image of a perfect servant; \n 4976 refers to the external, which is #腓 2:8 | The human body',	1),
(3357,	'05861',	'同义词\n\n   见 makrothumia 的定义     3115\n   见 hupomone 的定义        5281\n\n   5281 指一种特质, 就是在困苦中不会轻易屈服; \n   3115 是自我的节制, 不会急急忙忙的, 以错误的方式报复. \n        它和胆怯, 或失望,或其他有关愤怒, 报复, 等是相对的.',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of makrothumia 3115\n See definition of hupomone 5281\n\n 5281 refers to a trait that does not give in easily in hardship; \n 3115 is self-restraint, not in a hurry, to retaliate in the wrong way. \n It and timidity, or disappointment, or anything else related to anger, revenge, etc are relative.',	1),
(3358,	'05860',	'同义词\n\n   见 kopos 的定义          2873\n   见 mochthos 的定义       3449\n   见 ponos 的定义          4192\n\n   4192 - 这种劳苦是辛勤工作的结果 (需要出力的工作)\n   2873 - 指劳累\n   3449 - 指辛苦, 艰辛 (主要是诗体)',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of kopos 2873\n See definition of mochthos 3449\n See definition of ponos 4192\n\n 4192 - This labor is the result of hard work (work that requires effort)\n 2873 - Refers to exhaustion\n 3449 - Refers to hard work, hardship (mainly poetic)',	1),
(3359,	'05859',	'同义词\n\n   见 kolasis 的定义        2851\n   见 timoria 的定义        5098\n\n   2851 和 5098 不同,  \n   2851 是指惩戒, 且指的是受惩戒的人所受的苦; \n   而5089 则是惩罚, 且指的是惩戒的人满意于他所施行的惩戒',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of kolasis 2851\n See definition of timoria 5098\n\n 2851 and 5098 are different, \n 2851 means discipline, and refers to the suffering suffered by a disciplined person; \n 5089 is punishment, and means that the person disciplining is satisfied with the discipline he has imposed',	1),
(3360,	'05858',	'同义词\n\n   见 keramos 的定义        2766\n   见 mignumi 的定义        3396\n\n   2766 - 较严格的看法, 指的是混合一些成份而成为一个新的复合物, 是化学方面的混合\n   3396 - 指的是把一些东西搅拌在一起, 或是将它们混合起来, 混杂在一起, 是机械式的混合',	'synonyms\n\n See definition of keramos 2766\n See definition of mignumi 3396\n\n 2766 - The stricter view, which refers to the mixing of some components into a new compound, is the mixing of chemical aspects\n 3396 - Refers to mixing things together, or mixing them together, mixing them together, is mechanical mixing',	1),
