(4058,	'05844',	'同义词\n\n   见 entellomai      1781\n   见 keleuo          2753\n   见 paraggello      3853\n   见 tasso           5021\n\n   1781 - 吩咐--通常出自于那些有发号施令权位的人,\n   重点在命令的内容:\"我们的指示\"\n   2753 - 命令--口头发号施令,通常出于上司或长官的口\n   3853 - 下令--特别是军队的长官对部队下达命令\n   5021 - 指派--通常是军中任命,含有相关职责\n\n   3853与1781的不同在于指的是固定长久的任务,而非特殊\n   或是偶而发出的命令,其职责是出于自己的位阶,并非出自\n   长官的个人意愿',	'synonyms\n\n See entellomai 1781\n See Keleuo 2753\n See paraggello 3853\n See tasso 5021\n\n 1781 - Orders - usually from those who have the authority to issue orders,\n Focus on the content of the command: “Our instructions”\n 2753 - Order — Order by mouth, usually by the mouth of a superior or officer\n 3853 - Orders — especially the chief of the army giving orders to the troops\n 5021 - Assignment—usually an appointment in the military, with related duties\n\n The difference between 3853 and 1781 is that it refers to fixed and permanent tasks rather than special\n or an occasional order whose duties are based on one\'s own rank, not from\n Personal wishes of the chief',	1),
