(5538,	'02316',	'2316 theos {theh\'-os}\n\n不确定相似的字源; 神, (与 03588 一起) 特别是至高无上的神;\n   TDNT - 3:65,322; 阳性名词\n\n钦定本 - God 1320, God 13, godly 3, God-ward + 4214 2, misc 5; 1343\n\n1) 神或女神, 神或神格的统称\n2) 神性, 三位一体\n   2a) 上帝天父, 三位一体的第一位\n   2b) 基督, 三位一体的第二位\n   2c) 圣灵, 三位一体的第三位\n3) 神 (用来形容值得特别尊敬的对象)\n   3a) 人 (#约 10:34|)\n   3b) 肚腹 (#腓 3:19|)\n4) 魔鬼 (#林后 4:4|)',	'2316 theos {theh\'-os}\n\nUnsure of similar etymology; God, (together with 03588) especially the supreme god;\n TDNT - 3:65 ,322; positive noun\n\nAdorned Book - God 1320, God 13, godly 3, God-ward +4214 2, misc 5; 1343\n\n1) A general term for a god or goddess, god or deity\n2) Divinity, Trinity\n 2a) God Heavenly Father, First in the Trinity\n 2b) Christ, Second Person in the Trinity\n 2c) Holy Spirit, Third Person of the Trinity\n3) God (used to describe an object worthy of special respect)\n 3a) People (#约 10:34 |)\n 3b) Belly (#腓 3:19 |)\n4) Devil (#林后 4:4 |)',	1),
(5539,	'02412',	'2412 hieroprepes {hee-er-op-rep-ace\'}\n\n源自 02413 以及与 04241 同源的字; TDNT - 3:253,349; 形容词\n\n钦定本 - as becometh holiness 1; 1\n\n1) 对上帝适当的人, 地点, 行为或神圣的事物\n2) 恭敬虔诚的 (#多 2:3|)',	'2412 hieroprepes {hee-er-op-rep-ace\'}\n\nFrom 02413 and words homologous to 04241; TDNT - 3:253 ,349; adjectives\n\nQindingben - as becometh holiness 1; 1\n\n1) A person appropriate to God, place, act or sacred thing\n2) Respectful and pious (#多 2:3 |)',	1),
(5540,	'02418',	'2418 hierourgeo {hee-er-oorg-eh\'-o}\n\n源自 02411 与 02041 字根的复合型; TDNT - 3:251,349; 动词\n\n钦定本 - minister 1; 1\n\n1) 执行祭司或神圣的职分 (#罗 15:16|)',	'2418 hierourgeo {hee-er-oorg-eh\'-o}\n\nComplex from 02411 and 02041 roots; TDNT - 3:251 ,349; verb\n\nThe definitive book - 1; 1\n\n1) Perform priesthood or sacred duties (#罗 15:16 |)',	1),
(5541,	'02839',	'2839 koinos {koy-nos\'}\n\n可能源自 04862; TDNT - 3:789,447; 形容词\n\n钦定本 - common 7, unclean 3, defiled 1, unholy 1; 12\n\n1) 共通的, 共同的\n2) 平常的, 普通的, 凡俗的\n   2a) 礼仪上不洁的',	'2839 koinos {koy-nos\'}\n\nMay derive from 04862; TDNT - 3:789 ,447; adjective\n\nQindingben - common 7, unclean 3, defiled 1, unholy 1; 12\n\n1) Common, joint\n2) Ordinary, ordinary, mundane\n 2a) Unclean etiquette',	1),
(5542,	'03004',	'3004 lego {leg\'-o}\n\n字根字; TDNT - 4:69,505; 动词\n\n钦定本 - say 1184, speak 61, call 48, tell 33, misc 17; 1343\n\n1) (以口头或书面表达) 说, 告诉, 表述\n2) (以具体的方式表达) 说\n   2a) 问\n   2b) 回答\n   2c) 命令, 勉励, 劝告, 引导\n   2d) 断言, 保证\n   2e) 主张, 宣布, 声称\n3) 告知, 通知\n4) 称呼, 叫名字',	'3004 lego {leg\'-o}\n\nroot word; TDNT - 4:69 ,505; verb\n\nQindingben - say 1184, speak 61, call 48, tell 33, misc 17; 1343\n\n1) Say, tell, express (either orally or in writing)\n2) Say (in a specific way)\n 2a) Ask\n 2b) Answer\n 2c) Order, encourage, advise, guide\n 2d) Assertions, guarantees\n 2e) assert, declare, claim\n3) Notice, notice\n4) Name, name',	1),
(5543,	'03123',	'3123 mallon {mal\'-lon}\n\n与 03122 相同的中性比较级; 副词 比较级\n\n钦定本 - more 34, rather 33, the more 12, better + 2570 2, misc 4; 85\n\n1) 更加\n2) 宁愿, 宁可, 更确定\n3) 反而, 取而代之',	'3123 mallon {mal\'-lon}\n\nSame neutral comparison ratings as 03122; Adverb comparisons\n\nChinding book - more 34, rather 33, the more 12, better + 2570 2, misc 4; 85\n\n1) More\n2) Prefer, Prefer, Be More Sure\n3) Instead, take its place',	1),
