(5545,	'04074',	'4074 Petros {pet\'-ros}\n\n显然是个基本字; TDNT - 6:100,835; 阳性专有名词 人名\n\n钦定本 - Peter 161, stone 1; 162\n\n彼得 = \"岩石\" 或 \"石头\"\n1) 耶稣的十二个门徒之一',	'4074 Petros {pet\'-ros}\n\nApparently a basic word; TDNT - 6:100 ,835; positive proper noun person\'s name\n\nThe definitive book - Peter 161, stone 1; 162\n\nPeter = “rock” or “stone”\n1) One of the twelve disciples of Jesus',	1),
