(5547,	'04736',	'4736 Stephanos {stef\'-an-os}\n\n与 04735 同源; 阳性专有名词 人名\n\n钦定本 - Stephen 7; 7\n\n司提反 = \"带冠冕的\"\n1) 耶路撒冷教会七个执事之一, 第一位基督徒殉教士',	'4736 Stephanos {stef\'-an-os}\n\nSame origin as 04735; positive proper noun name\n\nAdmiration Book - Stephen 7; 7\n\nStetam = “crowned”\n1) One of the seven deacons of the Church of Jerusalem, the first Christian martyr',	1),
