(5550,	'00652',	'652 apostolos {ap-os\'-tol-os}\n\n源自 0649; TDNT - 1:407,67; 阳性名词\n\n钦定本 - apostle 78, messenger 2, he that is sent 1; 81\n\n1) 代表, 使者, 受命令差派的人\n2) (神的) 使者\n   2a) 先知\n   2b) 基督 (#来 3:1|)\n   2c) 主要指新约时代一群受尊敬, 有特别使命的信徒',	'652 apostolos {ap-os\'-tol-os}\n\nDerived from 0649; TDNT - 1:407,67; positive noun\n\nChin Dingben - apostle 78, messenger 2, he that is sent 1; 81\n\n1) Representative, messenger, person sent by order\n2) (God\'s) Messenger\n 2a) Prophet\n 2b) Christ (#来 3:1 |)\n 2c) Primarily refers to a group of respected believers with a special mission in the New Testament era',	1),
(5551,	'00700',	'700 aresko {ar-es\'-ko}\n\n可能源自 0142 (取其情绪激动的意思); TDNT - 1:455,77; 动词\n\n钦定本 - please 17; 17\n\n1) 取悦, 奉承 (#加 1:10; 帖前 2:4|)\n2) 讨好, 顺应',	'700 aresko {ar-es\'-ko}\n\nMay be derived from 0142 (take the meaning of emotional excitement); TDNT - 1:455 ,77; verb\n\nThe definitive book - please 17; 17\n\n1) Pleasure, Flattery (#加 1:10; 2:4 |)\n2) Pleasure, conformist',	1),
