(5553,	'05561',	'5561 chora {kho\'-rah}\n\n源自 05490 的字根的衍生字, 取其\"空着的广阔区域\"之意; 阴性名词\n\n钦定本 - country 15, region 5, land 3, field 2, ground 1, coast 1; 27\n\n1) 陆地 (#徒 27:27|)\n2) 地区, 区域, 地方\n3) 乡下\n4) 田地, 耕地\n5) 地方 (#太 4:16|) \n\n同义词见 05875',	'5561 chora {kho\'-rah}\n\nDerived from the root of 05490, meaning “an empty vast area”; a negative noun\n\nChindingbon - country 15, region 5, land 3, field 2, ground 1, coast 1; 27\n\n1) Land (#徒 27:27 |)\n2) Regions, Regions, Provinces\n3) Countryside\n4) Fields, arable land\n5) Local (#太 4:16 |) \n\nSee 05875 for synonyms',	1),
(5554,	'01247',	'1247 diakoneo {dee-ak-on-eh\'-o}\n\n源于 01249; TDNT - 2:81,152; 动词\n\n钦定本 - minister unto 15, serve 10, minister 7, misc 5; 37\n\n1) 中介人/代理人, 听使唤\n2) 履行义务\n   2a) 服侍, 执行责任, 从旁辅助\n   2b) 伺候 (用餐)\n3) 帮助 (即时的需要)\n4) 执行公务\n5) 照料 (#徒 6:2|)',	'1247 diakoneo {dee-ak-on-eh\'-o}\n\nFrom 01249; TDNT - 2:81 ,152; verb\n\nQindingben - unto 15, serve 10, 7, misc 5; 37\n\n1) Intermediator/agent, listen to the call\n2) Fulfilling obligations\n 2a) Serving, performing duties, assisting from the side\n 2b) Serving (dining)\n3) Help (immediate need)\n4) Perform official duties\n5) Care (#徒 6:2 |)',	1),
