(5565,	'05495',	'5495 cheir {khire}\n\n可能源于 05494, 取其同意字 05490 字意 (取其\"净空以抓取\"之意); TDNT - 9:424,1309; 阴性名词\n\n钦定本 - hand 178, not tr 1; 179\n\n1) 手\n2) ...之手\n   2a) 藉由某人或某人的行动\n   2b) 神的手: 意谓神的能力\n   2c) 敌对的势力',	'5495 cheir {khire}\n\nMay have originated from 05494, taking its concurrence word 05490 (meaning “headroom to grab”); TDNT - 9:424 ,1309; negative noun\n\nChin Dingben - hand 178, not tr 1; 179\n\n1) Hands\n2) The hand of...\n 2a) Through the actions of a person or\n 2b) Hand of God: Meaning God\'s Power\n 2c) Hostile forces',	1),
(5566,	'05548',	'5548 chrio {khree\'-o}\n\n可能近似于 05530, 取其\"接触\"之意; TDNT - 9:493,1322; 动词\n\n钦定本 - anoint 5; 5\n\n1) 以油膏膏之\n   1a) 封予耶稣弥赛亚的职分, 并赐予他行事所需的权柄\n   1b) 指基督徒承受圣灵的膏抹 (#林后 1:21|)\n\n其同义字, 见 05805',	'5548 chrio {khree\'-o}\n\nMay be approximated to 05530, meaning “contact”; TDNT - 9:493 ,1322; verb\n\nAdmiration Book - anoint 5; 5\n\n1) Ointment\n 1a) Proclaim the duties of Jesus as the Messiah and give him the authority necessary to act\n 1b) Refers to Christians being anointed by the Holy Spirit (#林后 1:21 |)\n\nFor synonyms, see 05805',	1),
(5567,	'00018',	'18 agathos {ag-ath-os\'}\n\na primary word; TDNT - 1:10,3; 形容词\n\n钦定本 - good 77, good thing 14, that which is good+3588 8,\n     the thing which is good+3588 1, well 1, benefit 1; 102\n\n1) 优质的\n 1a)有用的,有益的\n 1b)好东西,财物\n2) 极有价值,优点的\n形容词 \n 2a)形容神只或人\n 2b)形容东西,特别是其社会性的意义与价值\n实名词\n 2c)有好处的,有帮助的\n 2d)好行为 (#约 5:29|)',	'18 agathos {ag-ath-os\'}\n\na primary word; TDNT - 1:10 ,3; adjective\n\nQindingben - good 77, good thing 14, that which is good+3588 8,\n the thing which is good+3588 1, well 1, benefit 1; 102\n\n1) High quality\n 1a) useful, beneficial\n 1b) goodies, belongings\n2) Extremely valuable, advantageous\nadjectives \n 2a) Describe God only or people\n 2b) Describe something, especially its social meaning and value\nReal nouns\n 2c) Helpful, Helpful\n 2d) Good Behavior (#约 5:29 |)',	1),
