(5570,	'00337',	'337 anaireo {an-ahee-reh\'-o}\n\n源于 0303 和 0138 的主动与态; 动词\n\n钦定本 - kill 10, slay 8, put to death 2, take up 1, do 1, take away 1; 23\n\n1) 挪走 (#来 10:9|) \n2) 消除, 毁灭\n3) 拿起, 据为己有 (#徒 7:21|)',	'337 anaireo {an-ahee-reh\'-o}\n\nActive and state; verbs derived from 0303 and 0138\n\nChindingben - kill 10, slay 8, put to death 2, take up 1, do 1, take away 1; 23\n\n1) Take Away (#来 10:9 |) \n2) Eliminate, destroy\n3) Pick it up, take it for yourself (#徒 7:21 |)',	1);
