(5600,	'01377',	'1377 dioko {dee-o\'-ko}\n\n字根型动词 dio (\"逃跑\"; 参 01169 的字根和 01249) 的扩展 (及使役) 型;\n   TDNT - 2:229,177; 动词\n\n钦定本 - persecute 28, follow after 6, follow 4,\n     suffer persecution 3, misc 3; 44\n\n1) 急忙, 跑, 奋勇向前\n2) 迫害 (因着信仰)\n3) 驱离, 赶走\n4) 追逐, 追求',	'1377 dioko {dee-o\'-en}\n\nThe extended (and active) type of the root verb dio (“escape”; see the root of 01169 and 01249);\n TDNT - 2:229 ,177; verb\n\nAdmiration Book - ute 28, follow after 6, follow 4,\n 3, misc 3; 44\n\n1) Hurry, run, and move forward courageously\n2) Persecution (because of faith)\n3) Evict, drive away\n4) Chase, pursue',	1),
