(5784,	'01722',	'1722 en {en}\n\n原型介系词, 表 (固定的) 位置 (在某个地点, 时间, 或状态),\n和 (隐喻) 凭藉用法 (中间的或结构性的), 亦即：与其余的一种关系\n (介于 01519 和 01537 之间); TDNT - 2:537,233; 介系词\n\n钦定本- in 1874, by 141, with 134, among 117, at 112, on 46,\n     through 37, misc 321; 2782\n\n1) 接间接受格:\n   在...里, 藉着, 靠 (#太 12:24|), 用, 在...之上, 在...附近, \n   旁边, 在...前, 在...当中, 在...里面, 进入 (=eis), 向... (罕用), \n   穿 (#太 11:8|), 指着 (#太 23:16|), 奉 (#太 23:39|)\n2) en tw 接不定词:\n   在...期间, 当...时 (#太 11:24|), 按时 (#太 21:41|)\n\nWigram\'s 出现次数: 2798 不是 2782.',	'1722 en {en}\n\narchetypal mesonym, table (fixed) location (in a place, time, or state),\nand (metaphor) by usage (intermediate or structural), ie: a relationship with the rest\n (between 01519 and 01537); TDNT - 2:537 ,233; mesons\n\nChinding Book- in 1874, by 141, with 134, among 117, at 112, on 46,\n through 37, misc 321; 2782\n\n1) Indirect acceptance:\n In..., by, by (#太 12:24 |), with, on, in the vicinity of, \n Next to, in front of, in, in, in (=eis), towards... (rare), \n Wear (#太 11:8 |), Pointing (#太 23:16 |), Bong (#太 23:39 |)\n2) en tw join infinitive:\n During..., when (#太 11:24 |), on time (#太 21:41 |)\n\nWigram\'s occurrences: 2798 not 2782.',	1),
