(5896,	'04270',	'4270 prographo {prog-raf\'-o}\n\n源自 4253 与 1125; TDNT - 1:770,128; 动词\n\nAV - write 1, write aforetime 1, write afore 1,\n     evidently set forth 1, before ordain 1; 5\n\n1) 事先写下\n 1a) 同一个文本里 (#弗 3:3)\n 1b) 以前写的,在旧有的记录里 (#罗 15:4; 犹4|)\n2) 公开的刻画,描绘,宣告 (#加 3:1|)\n\n   2b) 在众人面前刻画, 描绘, 绘画',	'4270 prographo {prog-raf\'-o}\n\nFrom 4253 vs 1125; TDNT - 1:770,128; verb\n\nAV - write 1, write aforetime 1, write afore 1,\n Evidently set forth 1, before ordain 1; 5\n\n1) Write it down in advance\n 1a) In the same text (#弗 3:3)\n 1b) written before, in the old records (#罗 15:4; Jew 4|)\n2) Public portrayal, depiction, and proclamation (#加 3:1 |)\n\n 2b) Portray, depict, paint in front of the crowd',	1),
